    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Tooth-bearing portions of jaw bones in Hyphessobrycon sateremawe, paratype, INPA 50729, 24.3 mm SL. A) Mesial view of premaxillary, right side. B) mesial view of distal portion of lower jaw, right side. C) lateral view of distal portion of maxillary, right side. Scale bar: 0.5 mm." ;
